
sample_ktc: Show how to use KTC to transfer a key to SOC key destination 2

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_ktc.img

To trigger key export:
$ cmtest data -f100 ""

Expected return value OK.
Expected QEMU log messages:
KTC: Destination 0x00000002
KTC: Allowed destinations 0x0000ffff
KTC: Total block num 16
KTC: Block 0
...
KTC: tx complete

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
